snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Dark Hunter - Shita Youma no Mori (1997)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Dark Hunter: Shita Youma no Mori is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Koei, which was released in Japan in 1997.
